text.text: This is a public waterpark for children age 12 and below. It is situated at Blk307 Yishun Ring Road. It is beside a HDB carpark. Operated from 9:30am. It has male and female washrooms and rooms for showers. It is a gated area.

text.text: Went here expecting full waterplay but button to turn on water was not working? There was no water coming out even though we pressed it very long. Kid could only play with the wading pond. Called for help from town council but no one came to help. They said some of the equipement is spoilt. Then maybe put up notice or smth so we won't make a wasted trip? Disappointed.

text.text: A great place for families to hang out with their kids! My 2 year old toddler loves it here. There are water features for every age group from 0-10 years old to enjoy. There are also ample sitting areas and tables for the adults to hang out and chill.
